title: Howard Stern 7-2-14
description:
Sorry about the file sizes and the separate parts, this is my first time doing this. I had the recording quality set too high so they are big files, but hey, its better than nothing right? The end of Sternthology has about 30 min of another show because I fell asleep while recording and I'm having issues with my programs right now so I couldn't chop the end off. I figured I'd share this here since no one has been uploading the show. I don't have the days we are missing, unfortunately. I don't think there are any commercials in these but if I do it in the future there probably will be because I'll just record while at work. I'll try to keep posting as long as it doesn't become a pain in the ass.

This file has: The full show, wrap up, Sternthology, Leiberman Live



~Phoenix
